","line":118},{"title":"Derendil","target":"Derendil","line":119},{"title":"Stool","target":"Stool","line":120},{"title":"Topsy","target":"Topsy","line":121},{"title":"Turvy","target":"Turvy","line":122},{"title":"Roxanne","target":"Roxanne","line":123},{"title":"Clementine","target":"Clementine","line":124},{"title":" Drow / Elite Warrior     | Velkynvelve garrison                            | Multi-attacked Kit repeatedly, critted her for 24 damage                                   | Velkynvelve cavern floor | Alive (wounded)                 |\n\n### Reputation & Relationships\n\n- **Quaggoth allegiance shifted to Derendil.** The quaggoths recognized Derendil as the new alpha after Ilvara's fall. They turned on the remaining drow mid-combat — attacking Asha and the Drow Elite. This fundamentally changes the power dynamic at Velkynvelve.\n- **Jorlan Duskryn confirmed as ally.** His crossbow shot and smile at Ilvara's impalement cement him as a genuine turncoat, not a one-time opportunist. His motivations remain personal (grudge against Ilvara) but his actions saved the party.\n- **Turvy's loyalty deepened.** His Silver Barbs save on Kit — \"Can't lose anymore\" — demonstrates his commitment to the party beyond his conditional terms from S06.\n\n---\n\n## Artifacts\n\n### Loot & Items\n\n| Character / Owner | Item / Artifact | State / Context |\n|---|---|---|\n| No new loot acquired | — | Pure combat session. Potential loot from Ilvara and Shoor's bodies not yet addressed — likely S14. |\n\n*Trinket empowerment stat bonuses confirmed pre-session (see House Rules). Not new items — updates to existing growth items.*\n\n---\n\n## Logs\n\n### Encounters\n\n| Enemies | Location | Party / Allies Present | Trigger | Outcome |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Ilvara Mizzrym, Shoor Vandree, Asha Vandree, Drow Elite, Drow E, 2 Giant Spiders, 2+ Quaggoths | Velkynvelve cavern floor | Full party + Topsy, Turvy, Roxy, Stool, Clementine; joined by Derendil and Jorlan mid-battle | Continuation from S12 assault | Ilvara killed (Roxy gore). Shoor killed (Ilvara's own Insect Plague). 1 giant spider killed (Turvy), 1 spider put to sleep (Topsy). Quaggoths switched sides. Asha fled (<10 HP). Drow Elite alive but wounded. |\n\n### Initiative\n\n*Combat 1 — Battle of Velkynvelve (Continuation from S12)*\n\nInitiative order carried over from S12. Key turn order as referenced in transcript:\n\n| Character / Creature | Turn Order |\n|---|---|\n| [[Ilvara Mizzrym","target":"Drow Elite (unnamed)","line":125},{"title":"Turvy","target":"Turvy","line":165},{"title":"Shoor Vandree","target":"Shoor Vandree","line":167},{"title":"Darby Stonefeather","target":"Darby Stonefeather","line":170},{"title":"Topsy","target":"Topsy","line":171},{"title":"Amanita de'Champignon","target":"Amanita de'Champignon","line":172},{"title":"Binks Stonevein","target":"Binks Stonevein","line":173},{"title":"Aeolus","target":"Aeolus","line":174},{"title":"Asha Vandree","target":"Asha Vandree","line":175},{"title":"Kit Aluri","target":"Kit Aluri","line":176},{"title":"Blarg","target":"Blarg","line":177},{"title":"Roxanne","target":"Roxanne","line":178},{"title":"Quote Board Master","target":"Quote Board Master","line":248},{"title":"04-World-Lore/Locations/Velkynvelve","target":"04-World-Lore/Locations/Velkynvelve","line":286},{"title":"Asha Vandree","target":"Asha Vandree","line":286},{"title":"Campaign Dashboard","target":"Campaign Dashboard","line":286},{"title":"Derendil","target":"Derendil","line":286},{"title":"Ilvara Mizzrym","target":"Ilvara Mizzrym","line":286},{"title":"Jorlan Duskryn","target":"Jorlan Duskryn","line":286},{"title":"Kit Aluri Journal","target":"Kit Aluri Journal","line":286},{"title":"Roxanne","target":"Roxanne","line":286},{"title":"Shoor Vandree","target":"Shoor Vandree","line":286},{"title":"Stool","target":"Stool","line":286}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
